title: Amiga Game Pack No.1 Edition_2 for WinUAE
description:
You remember the Amiga Game Packs for the WinUAE Amiga Emulator?

Well here is Issue 2, Games which were NOT INCLUDED in the first issue
Also included is the WinUAE Amiga Emulator Version 1.4, the first issue had Version 1.3 included and has been updated and had minor bugs removed and compatability improved
Along with this ISSUE 2 pack will be: 

Instructions for most of the games from BOTH Game pack issues
Walkthroughs and Hints and Cheats and Tips
Screenshots from the actual games being played on WinUAE
And of course every Kickstart Rom you will ever need to make your Amiga dreams come true

Do you remember scene groups like:

Fairlight
Scoopex
Kefrens
Melon
Crystal
The Silents
Skid Row
Paradox

and many... many more....

Do you remember hacking into AT&T&#039;s Satelites to spread the warez all over the globe, back then we called it Box&#039;ing. Thats when the pirate net was the ONLY international means of computing, and it was well before the Internet got properly grounded.

re-live the Cracktro&#039;s and the demos from all of the above groups and more (too many to mention here), they&#039;re all here in the 
Amiga Game Packs for the WinUAE Emulator (ISSUE 2)
